It’s a beautiful poem by Rumi titled ‘The Guest House’ and it so perfectly captures why we should welcome our darkest emotions like a cherished guest to our own home. (see vid) ⁣
⁣
I’m sharing this because this week on Mindvalley, we’re exploring one of the most important aspects of what it means to be human - healing our past wounds and achieving emotional mastery. ⁣
⁣
Yet, it’s something we were taught very little (if at all) in schools and if anything, today’s society teaches us the opposite. ⁣
⁣
We’re trained from young to mask and hide our pain, but it only encourages us to suppress those unresolved hurts. Sometimes for years - It’s the reason why so many people feel like they have holes to fill in their being, rather than feeling like whole human beings. 😔⁣
⁣
One of the most powerful tools that can help us release traumas, heal emotional wounds, and make peace with our past is the spiritual practice of Tapping.⁣
⁣
And to guide you in this fascinating healing modality is one of today’s most sought-after Tapping experts @jennifer_partridge, in her brand new Masterclass this week. ⁣
⁣
In the same way Rumi suggested in this poem, for us to invite our darkest emotions in rather than running away from them, Jennifer will be teaching you how to face, process, and release any of the emotional baggage weighing you down through the healing practice of Tapping.⁣
⁣
Sign up for free through the link in my bio. ☝️

How do you guys think I would react? (see vid)⁣
⁣
Think of the bump as “life” and the coffee in your cup as “your emotional weight”. And when life ‘bumps’ into us, something is bound to spill out. ⁣
⁣
If your emotional weight is heavy, it could be something negative like an angry outburst, an episode of self-doubt, or an angry word. ⁣
⁣
But if your emotions are lighter, you might just smile at the humor of a giant coffee stain on your shirt, because the 'bump' from life hardly costs you anything. Or maybe you go into a mode of acceptance and resolve when faced with bigger ‘bumps’ like the loss of a job, or bad news. ⁣
⁣
Watch the short video to see what I mean. ⁣
⁣
In this week’s brand new Masterclass, acclaimed tapping expert @jennifer_partridge will guide you through an immersive guided Tapping exercise to help you acknowledge, process, and release any past emotional traumas weighing you down. And in turn, gain a new level of emotional liberation and mastery.⁣
⁣
Join the FREE Masterclass through the link in my bio. ☝️

What it means to be a "Woman" or a "Man" in today's world has evolved. Watch this video - it's well worth your time. 
⠀
I'm a big fan of @gary_zukav and his book on spiritual partnerships has redefined how I think about my relationships with everyone around me. 
⠀
So I was delighted when Gary came on stage at Mindvalley Summit to share ideas from his latest book, Universal Human. One of the most thrilling ideas he shared was his concept of where today's female and today's male are evolving. He also speaks of feminine energy, masculine energy, and the way both energies dance together in a modern partnership. 
⠀
Watch this clip and share it with someone who needs to hear this. What are your thoughts? 
⠀
Let me know in the comments.

I wanted to reshare this viral video that I recorded before the pandemic that racked up some 50 million views around the world and got me in trouble with some major food companies. 
⠀
I filmed this in a typical upscale grocery store in Malaysia that carries big international brands because I wanted to show you firsthand some of the marketing traps and misleading labels of ‘healthy’ products you consume every single day. 
⠀
Most people are unaware of how much their food choices are shaped by powerful marketing forces. Big food brands manipulate you into putting junk in your body through smart packaging and dirty labeling tactics. 
⠀
Watch the video for a few to look out for. 👀
⠀
And this is just the tip of the iceberg when it comes to the deceit of the food and diet industries.
⠀
In my newly upgraded Masterclass with @ericedmeades this week, he will be revealing ​​more about how profit-driven food, exercise, and diet industries have deceived and sabotaged your health. 
⠀
He’ll also be sharing some powerful psychology and nutritional anthropology principles that will completely transform how you view food and what you can do to get your metabolism, health, and immunity rocking again.
⠀
Sign up through the link in my bio. ☝️
⠀
It's free.

node.text:
If you want to get your dream body like your favorite celebrity, it’s easy. 
⠀
All you need are the following:
⠀
A world-class personal trainer
⠀
A nutritionist to plan out every one of your meals
⠀
A personal chef to cook those meals for you at home
⠀
Access to a state-of-the-art gym 
⠀
2 hours a day at the gym ⠀
⠀
Ok, that was a little tongue-in-cheek of me. 😉
⠀
Those are Brules. The truth is, you don’t need any of those things to get the body of your dreams because there is a way to get there by only working out for 15-minutes, twice a week. (see vid)
⠀
So if you’ve never successfully stuck to a workout routine because you’re too busy or because you don’t have a gym membership, your excuses end here. 
⠀
As someone running a massive company, parenting two badass kids, writing 3 books, and speaking around the world, trust me when I say I’m busy as heck. 🚀
⠀
But 10x has allowed me to have a body in my 40s that’s better than what I had in my mid-20s with only 30 minutes of exercise a week. 
⠀
Why is it so effective? There are 10 reasons. Watch the short video to find out. 
⠀
And if you want to learn more, join the creators of 10x @lorenzo_delano and @ronandiegoinsta in their FREE Masterclass. (link in bio)
⠀
As participants of this Masterclass, you’ll be invited to an exclusive 90-day total body transformation challenge that will completely change your life. 
⠀
You won’t want to miss it. Just click the link in my bio. ☝️

Every Sunday, my 7-year-old daughter, Eve does 10x with me. (voluntarily because she’s a badass 💪)

In this short video, Eve and Ronan demonstrate the 6 most effective exercises that have been scientifically proven to create the biggest impact on your body. (see vid) 

These are some of the exercises in the 10x program and it only takes two 15-minute workouts a week to gain optimal fitness. 

I believe that we’ve created the single most efficient exercise protocol on the planet to supercharge your strength, agility, and longevity.

This took 4 years of in-depth R&D, countless experiments on 100+ test subjects (both men and women, young and old, beginners and experienced), and cycling through FIVE iterations of this protocol. 

10x is a far more effective muscle-building protocol than anything else on the market.

If you’re excited to learn more, join me, @ronandiegoinsta, and @lorenzo_delano in a FREE Masterclass this week that will shatter your preconceived notions of what it means to ‘get fit.’ (link in bio ☝️)

P.S. When you join this Masterclass, you’ll also be one of the first in the world to receive a special invite to a global 10x body transformation challenge. 😉

P.P.S. If Eve can do it, so can you.

Honored to be able to interview the brilliant and renown Sadhguru. In addition to his profound spiritual wisdom, I just had to ask him about his beard. ⁣
⁣
Why do Indian sages never use beard wax or trim their beards? I've gotten to know Mahatria, Sri Sri Ravishankar and now Sadhguru. So much respect for them all. But why the wild beards? I had to know. Watch this man's beautiful and funny reply when I ask him about this. ⁣
⁣
And this is what makes Sadhguru so special. Wisdom with humor. Check this out. ⁣
⁣
Also check out his beautiful new book Karma: A Yogi's Guide to Crafting Your Destiny. Available on Amazon and bookstores everywhere.

And here’s where we need your help. We are about to launch our new program Mindvalley Pro and we don’t have a tagline, so…..

I’ll write a cheque for $5,000 to the person who comes up with a tagline that we decide to use on our site. 
⠀
So join the challenge and comment your best Mindvalley tagline down below. 
⠀
love you guys 🙏

It’s a beautiful poem by Rumi titled ‘The Guest House’ and it so perfectly captures why we should welcome our darkest emotions like a cherished guest to our own home. (see vid) ⁣
⁣
I’m sharing this because this week on Mindvalley, we’re exploring one of the most important aspects of what it means to be human - healing our past wounds and achieving emotional mastery. ⁣
⁣
Yet, it’s something we were taught very little (if at all) in schools and if anything, today’s society teaches us the opposite. ⁣
⁣
We’re trained from young to mask and hide our pain, but it only encourages us to suppress those unresolved hurts. Sometimes for years - It’s the reason why so many people feel like they have holes to fill in their being, rather than feeling like whole human beings. 😔⁣
⁣
One of the most powerful tools that can help us release traumas, heal emotional wounds, and make peace with our past is the spiritual practice of Tapping.⁣
⁣
And to guide you in this fascinating healing modality is one of today’s most sought-after Tapping experts @jennifer_partridge, in her brand new Masterclass this week. ⁣
⁣
In the same way Rumi suggested in this poem, for us to invite our darkest emotions in rather than running away from them, Jennifer will be teaching you how to face, process, and release any of the emotional baggage weighing you down through the healing practice of Tapping.⁣
⁣
Sign up for free through the link in my bio. ☝️

How do you guys think I would react? (see vid)⁣
⁣
Think of the bump as “life” and the coffee in your cup as “your emotional weight”. And when life ‘bumps’ into us, something is bound to spill out. ⁣
⁣
If your emotional weight is heavy, it could be something negative like an angry outburst, an episode of self-doubt, or an angry word. ⁣
⁣
But if your emotions are lighter, you might just smile at the humor of a giant coffee stain on your shirt, because the 'bump' from life hardly costs you anything. Or maybe you go into a mode of acceptance and resolve when faced with bigger ‘bumps’ like the loss of a job, or bad news. ⁣
⁣
Watch the short video to see what I mean. ⁣
⁣
In this week’s brand new Masterclass, acclaimed tapping expert @jennifer_partridge will guide you through an immersive guided Tapping exercise to help you acknowledge, process, and release any past emotional traumas weighing you down. And in turn, gain a new level of emotional liberation and mastery.⁣
⁣
Join the FREE Masterclass through the link in my bio. ☝️

⠀
I'm a big fan of @gary_zukav and his book on spiritual partnerships has redefined how I think about my relationships with everyone around me. 
⠀
So I was delighted when Gary came on stage at Mindvalley Summit to share ideas from his latest book, Universal Human. One of the most thrilling ideas he shared was his concept of where today's female and today's male are evolving. He also speaks of feminine energy, masculine energy, and the way both energies dance together in a modern partnership. 
⠀
Watch this clip and share it with someone who needs to hear this. What are your thoughts? 
⠀
Let me know in the comments.

node.text:
Back from Cappadocia, Turkey. One of the most amazing places to visit in the world. Crossed this one off my bucket list. 

Huge appreciation to the wonderful culture and people of Turkey 🇹🇷 and prayers for everyone affected by the wildfires (now mostly under control). 

Next spots on my bucket list include Nepal, Greenland, Bhutan, Alaska. What’s a place your dream of visiting?

node.text:
Attending the “Echoes from Agartha”music festival in Cappadocia, Turkey while dressed as a techno-shaman and experimenting with Mezcal and magic chocolate and dancing till sunrise and bonding with strangers and getting desert sand in every corner of my body turned out to be a totally good idea. Who would have guessed? 

Probably never saying no to music festival invites from friends again.

I wanted to reshare this viral video that I recorded before the pandemic that racked up some 50 million views around the world and got me in trouble with some major food companies. 
⠀
I filmed this in a typical upscale grocery store in Malaysia that carries big international brands because I wanted to show you firsthand some of the marketing traps and misleading labels of ‘healthy’ products you consume every single day. 
⠀
Most people are unaware of how much their food choices are shaped by powerful marketing forces. Big food brands manipulate you into putting junk in your body through smart packaging and dirty labeling tactics. 
⠀
Watch the video for a few to look out for. 👀
⠀
And this is just the tip of the iceberg when it comes to the deceit of the food and diet industries.
⠀
In my newly upgraded Masterclass with @ericedmeades this week, he will be revealing ​​more about how profit-driven food, exercise, and diet industries have deceived and sabotaged your health. 
⠀
He’ll also be sharing some powerful psychology and nutritional anthropology principles that will completely transform how you view food and what you can do to get your metabolism, health, and immunity rocking again.
⠀
Sign up through the link in my bio. ☝️
⠀
It's free.

node.text:
Estonian summer sunsets are amazing. 

This weekend I was honored to be asked to train and guide the audience at the “Good Life Festival” (“Hea Elu” in Estonian) i 

I took the audience through a training on the Six Phase Meditation.

I’m always impressed at how much Estonians are into Yoga, meditation, healthy eating and personal growth. There is a rumor that the Dalai Lama commented upon visiting Estonia that this is one of the few countries he’s seen with the energy similar to Tibet. And the people here reflect that. 

Congrats to @rolandtokko and Merit Raju for making this event happen. 

If you’re curious on the Six Phase Meditation google it and you’ll find tons of resources online. Its my daily morning practice that gives the results of hours of meditation in 15 mins. A major book on the Six Phase by Penguin-Randomhouse publishers will also be out next summer :)

If you’ve tried the Six Phase let me know what you think in comments 🙏

What does it take to truly feel rich?⁣
⁣
Sharing an idea here from Japanese money master Ken Honda on what it takes to truly be rich. I loved this idea and incorporated it into my mental models of life ⁣
⁣
if you like this I invite you to join me and @happykenhonda in Mindvalley’s free Masterclass this week to learn this crucial mental model about money. ⁣
⁣
This powerful mindset will allow you to finally make peace with your money and build the wealth you desire. ⁣
⁣
Sign up through the link in my bio. ☝️

node.text:
Stopped by Berlin to meet up with Mindvalley members. What an amazing group of people and an amazing time. Please tag members you know. 

As the world opens up Mindvalley members meetups will be blossoming all over the world.  And festivals , parties , and spectacular events like Mindvalley University are roaring back.

Every time I meet Mindvalley members I’m so impressed by their energy, their stories and their desire to create change in the world.

Thanks for an amazing time Berlin members 🙏🇩🇪

Where would you like to see the next meetup ?
